{"id":22,"parent_id":1,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":22,"title":"Genesis 21","subtitle":"","short_title":"Gen.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 21"],[".studySummary",["i","Sarah bears Isaac—He is circumcised—Hagar and her son are cast out of Abraham’s household—The Lord saves Hagar and Ishmael—Abraham and Abimelech deal honorably with each other."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.1","order":"02.02.021.1898"},["b","1"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"visited"],"Sarah as he had said, and the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"did unto",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"Sarah"],"as he had spoken."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.2","order":"02.02.021.1899"},["b","2"],"For Sarah conceived, and bare Abraham a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"son"],"in his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"old"],"age, at the set",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"time"],"of which God had spoken to him."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.3","order":"02.02.021.1900"},["b","3"],"And Abraham called the name of his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"son"],"that was born unto him, whom Sarah bare to him, Isaac."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.4","order":"02.02.021.1901"},["b","4"],"And Abraham",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"circumcised"],"his son Isaac being eight days old, as God had commanded him."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.5","order":"02.02.021.1902"},["b","5"],"And Abraham was an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"hundred"],"years old, when his son Isaac was born unto him."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.6","order":"02.02.021.1903"},["b","6"],"¶And Sarah said, God hath made me to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"laugh"],",",["i","so that"],"all that hear will laugh with me."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.7","order":"02.02.021.1904"},["b","7"],"And she said, Who would have said unto Abraham, that Sarah should have given children suck? for I have born",["i","him"],"a son in his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"old"],"age."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.8","order":"02.02.021.1905"},["b","8"],"And the child grew, and was weaned: and Abraham made a great feast the",["i","same"],"day that Isaac was weaned."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.9","order":"02.02.021.1906"},["b","9"],"¶And Sarah saw the son of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"Hagar"],"the Egyptian, which she had",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"born"],"unto Abraham,",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"mocking"],"."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.10","order":"02.02.021.1907"},["b","10"],"Wherefore she said unto Abraham,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"Cast"],"out this bondwoman and her son: for the son of this bondwoman shall not be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"heir"],"with my son,",["i","even"],"with Isaac."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.11","order":"02.02.021.1908"},["b","11"],"And the thing was very grievous in Abraham’s sight because of his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"son"],"."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.12","order":"02.02.021.1909"},["b","12"],"¶And God said unto Abraham, Let it not be grievous in thy sight because of the lad, and because of thy bondwoman; in all that Sarah hath said unto thee, hearken unto her voice; for in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"Isaac"],"shall thy",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"seed"],"be called."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.13","order":"02.02.021.1910"},["b","13"],"And also of the son of the bondwoman will I make a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"nation"],", because he",["i","is"],"thy seed."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.14","order":"02.02.021.1911"},["b","14"],"And Abraham rose up early in the morning, and took bread, and a bottle of water, and gave",["i","it"],"unto Hagar, putting",["i","it"],"on her shoulder, and the child, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"sent"],"her away: and she departed, and wandered in the wilderness of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"Beer-sheba"],"."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.15","order":"02.02.021.1912"},["b","15"],"And the water was spent in the bottle, and she cast the child under one of the shrubs."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.16","order":"02.02.021.1913"},["b","16"],"And she went, and sat her down over against",["i","him"],"a good way off, as it were a bowshot: for she said, Let me not see the death of the child. And she sat over against",["i","him,"],"and lift up her voice, and wept."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.17","order":"02.02.021.1914"},["b","17"],"And God heard the voice of the lad; and the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"angel"],"of God called to Hagar out of heaven, and said unto her, What aileth thee, Hagar? fear not; for God hath heard the voice of the lad where he",["i","is."]],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.18","order":"02.02.021.1915"},["b","18"],"Arise, lift up the lad, and hold him in thine hand; for I will make him a great",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"nation"],"."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.19","order":"02.02.021.1916"},["b","19"],"And God",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"opened"],"her eyes, and she saw a well of water; and she went, and filled the bottle with water, and gave the lad drink."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.20","order":"02.02.021.1917"},["b","20"],"And God was with the lad; and he grew, and dwelt in the wilderness, and became an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"archer"],"."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.21","order":"02.02.021.1918"},["b","21"],"And he dwelt in the wilderness of Paran: and his mother took him a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"wife"],"out of the land of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"Egypt"],"."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.22","order":"02.02.021.1919"},["b","22"],"¶And it came to pass at that time, that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"Abimelech"],"and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"Phichol"],"the chief captain of his host spake unto Abraham, saying,",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_22c"},"God"],["i","is"],"with thee in all that thou doest:"],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.23","order":"02.02.021.1920"},["b","23"],"Now therefore swear unto me here by God that thou wilt not deal falsely with me, nor with my son, nor with my son’s son:",["i","but"],"according to the kindness that I have done unto thee, thou shalt do unto me, and to the land wherein thou hast sojourned."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.24","order":"02.02.021.1921"},["b","24"],"And Abraham said, I will swear."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.25","order":"02.02.021.1922"},["b","25"],"And Abraham",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"reproved"],"Abimelech because of a well of water, which Abimelech’s servants",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_25b"},"had"],"violently taken away."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.26","order":"02.02.021.1923"},["b","26"],"And Abimelech said, I wot not who hath done this thing: neither didst thou tell me, neither yet heard I",["i","of it,"],"but to day."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.27","order":"02.02.021.1924"},["b","27"],"And Abraham took sheep and oxen, and gave them unto Abimelech; and both of them",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"made"],"a covenant."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.28","order":"02.02.021.1925"},["b","28"],"And Abraham set seven ewe lambs of the flock by themselves."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.29","order":"02.02.021.1926"},["b","29"],"And Abimelech said unto Abraham, What",["i","mean"],"these seven ewe lambs which thou hast set by themselves?"],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.30","order":"02.02.021.1927"},["b","30"],"And he said, For",["i","these"],"seven ewe lambs shalt thou take of my hand, that they may be a witness unto me, that I have digged this",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_30a"},"well"],"."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.31","order":"02.02.021.1928"},["b","31"],"Wherefore he called that place",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_31a"},"Beer-sheba"],"; because there they sware both of them."],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.32","order":"02.02.021.1929"},["b","32"],"Thus they made a covenant at Beer-sheba:",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_32a"},"then"],"Abimelech rose up, and Phichol the chief captain of his host, and they returned into the land of the Philistines."],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.33","order":"02.02.021.1930"},["b","33"],"¶And",["i","Abraham"],"planted a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_33a"},"grove"],"in Beer-sheba, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_33b"},"called"],"there on the name of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_33c"},"everlasting"],"God."],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.34","order":"02.02.021.1931"},["b","34"],"And Abraham sojourned in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_34a"},"Philistines’"],"land many days."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.1a","order":"02.02.021.1932"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/30.22.22-23"},"Gen. 30:22 (22–23)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/2.21"},"1 Sam. 2:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.1b","order":"02.02.021.1934"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/17.19"},"Gen. 17:19"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/18.10.10,14"},"18:10 (10, 14)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.2a","order":"02.02.021.1936"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/24.36"},"Gen. 24:36"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.2b","order":"02.02.021.1938"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/old-age"},"TG Old Age"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.2c","order":"02.02.021.1940"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/17.21"},"Gen. 17:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.3a","order":"02.02.021.1942"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/16.15.11,15"},"Gen. 16:15 (11, 15)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/1.28"},"1 Chr. 1:28"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/seed-of-abraham"},"TG Seed of Abraham"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.4a","order":"02.02.021.1944"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/circumcision"},"TG Circumcision"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.5a","order":"02.02.021.1946"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/17.17"},"Gen. 17:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.6a","order":"02.02.021.1948"},["b","6a"],"The Hebrew root",["span.translit",["span.emphasis","tzachak"]],"means both “to laugh” and “to rejoice”; thus there is double meaning implied in its use here.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/gal/4.27"},"Gal. 4:27"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/132.56"},"D&C 132:56"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/laughter"},"TG Laughter"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.7a","order":"02.02.021.1950"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/18.12.11-12"},"Gen. 18:12 (11–12)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.9a","order":"02.02.021.1952"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/16.1"},"Gen. 16:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.9b","order":"02.02.021.1954"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/16.15"},"Gen. 16:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"9c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.9c","order":"02.02.021.1956"},["b","9c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/gal/4.29"},"Gal. 4:29"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.10a","order":"02.02.021.1958"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/gal/4.30"},"Gal. 4:30"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.10b","order":"02.02.021.1960"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/52.2"},"D&C 52:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.11a","order":"02.02.021.1962"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/17.18"},"Gen. 17:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.12a","order":"02.02.021.1964"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/17.40"},"1 Ne. 17:40"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.10"},"D&C 27:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.12b","order":"02.02.021.1966"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/abrahamic-covenant"},"TG Abrahamic Covenant"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/seed-of-abraham"},"Seed of Abraham"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.13a","order":"02.02.021.1968"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/seed-of-abraham"},"TG Seed of Abraham"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.14a","order":"02.02.021.1970"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/25.6"},"Gen. 25:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.14b","order":"02.02.021.1972"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.31"},"Gen. 21:31"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.17a","order":"02.02.021.1974"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/angels"},"TG Angels"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.18a","order":"02.02.021.1976"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/seed-of-abraham"},"TG Seed of Abraham"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.19a","order":"02.02.021.1978"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/6.20"},"2 Kgs. 6:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.20a","order":"02.02.021.1980"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/16.12"},"Gen. 16:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.21a","order":"02.02.021.1982"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/marriage-interfaith"},"TG Marriage, Interfaith"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.21b","order":"02.02.021.1984"},["b","21b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/16.1"},"Gen. 16:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.22a","order":"02.02.021.1986"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/20.2.1-16"},"Gen. 20:2 (1–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"22b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.22b","order":"02.02.021.1988"},["b","22b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/26.26"},"Gen. 26:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"22c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.22c","order":"02.02.021.1990"},["b","22c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/26.28"},"Gen. 26:28"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.25a","order":"02.02.021.1992"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/26.20"},"Gen. 26:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"25b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.25b","order":"02.02.021.1994"},["b","25b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/26.15.15-22"},"Gen. 26:15 (15–22)"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.27a","order":"02.02.021.1996"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/26.31.26-33"},"Gen. 26:31 (26–33)"],"."],["div",{"id":"30a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.30a","order":"02.02.021.1998"},["b","30a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/26.15"},"Gen. 26:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"31a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.31a","order":"02.02.021.2000"},["b","31a"],["span.small","IE"],"The well of the oath, or well of seven.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.14.14,32"},"Gen. 21:14 (14, 32)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/26.18,33"},"26:18, 33"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/46.1"},"46:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"32a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.32a","order":"02.02.021.2002"},["b","32a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/jst/jst-gen/21.31-32"},["span.small","JST"],"Gen. 21:31–32 (Appendix)"],"."],["div",{"id":"33a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.33a","order":"02.02.021.2004"},["b","33a"],["span.small","OR"],"tamarisk."],["div",{"id":"33b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.33b","order":"02.02.021.2006"},["b","33b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prayer"},"TG Prayer"],"."],["div",{"id":"33c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.33c","order":"02.02.021.2008"},["b","33c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/40.28"},"Isa. 40:28"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/16.26"},"Rom. 16:26"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.34"},"D&C 133:34"],"."],["div",{"id":"34a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.34a","order":"02.02.021.2010"},["b","34a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/10.14"},"Gen. 10:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/26.1"},"26:1"],"."]]}
